# neural-sudoku-comparative: the report keeps its figures and its result
# tables, but not the downloaded benchmark or the trained checkpoints, which
# `python -m experiments.run` regenerates.
!docs/neural/figures/*.pdf
docs/neural/sudoku_data/
docs/neural/artifacts/
docs/neural/*.pt
